OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fto the evening then cloud thickening
OL,7,Fto bring some outbreaks of mainly
OL,8,Flight rain, mostly to Shetland.
OL,9,FPerhaps some patchy haar. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FShetland cloudy with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain in the morning
OL,13,Fbecoming drier in the afternoon.
OL,14,FOrkney mostly dry and cloudy or bright.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry on Wednesday and Thursday, though
OL,18,Fhaar possible later. Increasing chance
OL,19,Fof some heavy rain or showers late
OL,20,FThursday or Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
